         <abstract id="aspace_27194cfd4f44d9f2750370e130ce699f">The papers consist chiefly of six sketchbooks of drawings and watercolors of Italian scenes and copies of old masters made by Truman Seymour after his retirement to Italy in 1876. Also included are two notebooks from 1885.</abstract>
